ntown%20Lima%2C%20Ohio%2C%20for%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shop%20sells%20comics%20and%20collectibles%20and%20frequently%20hosts%20community%20events%2C%20including%20an%20annual%20free%20comic%20book%20day%2C%20where%20they%20give%20away%20thousands%20of%20comics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20Bowker%20says%20he%20doesn't%20know%20what%20Monday%20will%20bring%2C%20given%20the%20whiplash%20of%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20tariff%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20suppliers%20are%20charging%20him%20as%20much%20as%2034%25%20more%20as%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20tariffs%2C%20some%20of%20which%20he's%20had%20to%20pass%20down%20to%20his%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20prices%20go%20up%20at%20your%20local%20small%20business%2C%20it's%20not%20because%20we%20want%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20because%20we're%20forced%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2070%25%20of%20Alter%20Ego's%20revenue%20comes%20from%20high-end%20collectibles%20based%20on%20characters%20from%20brands%20like%20Star%20Wars%2C%20Marvel%2C%20DC%20Comics%2C%20and%20Disney.%20Those%20products%20are%20made%20in%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20up%20to%20a%20245%25%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-dynamic-pricing-inflation-costs-china-trade-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20goods.%20Bowker%20said%20his%20profit%20margins%20have%20been%20slashed%20in%20half%20on%20many%20items%2C%20including%20some%20that%20were%20pre-ordered%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tariff%20is%20not%20being%20paid%20by%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20the%20tariff%20is%20being%20paid%20by%20the%20American%20consumer%20and%20the%20American%20small%20business%2C%20and%20the%20American%20company%20paying%20to%20have