l-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20products%20are%20being%20tested%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-industry-key-ukraine-postwar-economy-former-foreign-minister-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20defense%20tech%20industry%20has%20boomed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20drone%20and%20robotics%20makers%20to%20electronic%20warfare%20system%20providers%2C%20Ukrainian%20innovation%20has%20been%20on%20full%20display%20since%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20the%20country%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20company%20to%20have%20sprung%20up%20since%20the%20conflict%20began%20is%20Himera%2C%20which%20makes%20electronic%20warfare-resistant%20walkie-talkies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20products%20include%20the%20G1%20Pro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tactical%20handheld%20radio%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20B1%20repeater%2C%20which%20extends%20communication%20ranges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20only%20having%20launched%20in%202022%2C%20the%20company%20has%20quickly%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20defense%20tech%20industry%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product's%20major%20selling%20point%20is%20that%20it%20offers%20a%20potential%20solution%20to%20one%20of%20the%20defining%20challenges%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20electronic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G1%20is%20EW-resistant%2C%20using%20frequency-hopping%20technology%20to%20help%20evade%20electronic%20warfare%20interference%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20disrupt%20and%20jam%20certain%20signals%20like%20GPS%2C%20radio%2C%20and%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReticulate%20Micro%2C%20which%20supplies%20Himera's%20radios%20in%20the%20US%2C%20announced%20the%20first%20US%20delivery%20of%20G1%20Pro%20radios%20to%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20in%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20Air%20Force%20would%20test%20the%20G1%20Pro%20alongside%20Reticulate's%20Video%20Assured%20Secure%20Transmission%20(VAST)%20technology%2C%20which%20delivers%20real-time%20video%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Joshua%20Cryer%2C%20then%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20Reticulate%20Micro%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BBy%20combining%20the%20Himera%20G1%20Pro%20with%20VAST%2C%20we're%20aiming%20to%20democratize%20secure%20video%20transmission%20on%20the%20battlefield%E2%80%94empowering%20every%20warfighter%20with%20video-capable%20radio%20technology%20for%20enhanced%20situational%20awareness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMisha%20Rudominski%2C%20one%20of%20Himera's%20cofounders%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Himera's%20tech%20%26quot%3Bbridges%20the%20gap%26quot%3B%20between%20tactical%20and%20commercial%20communications%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20the%20best%20from%20both%20worlds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20all%20the%20tactical%20relevant%20functionality%20like%20low%20probability%20of%20detection%2C%20low%20probability%20of%20interception%2C%20and%20low%20probability%20of%20jamming%2C%20which%20you%20don't%20find%20in%20commercial%20spec%20solutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20do%20it%20in%20a%20very%20user-friendly%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20lightest%20radio%2C%20we%20have%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20battery%20lives%20on%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G1%20Pro%20has%20a%20battery%20life%20of%20around%2048%20hours%20and%20weighs%20just%20300%20grams.%20It%20can%20support%20the%20transmission%20of%20multiple%20information%20types%2C%20such%20as%20GPS%2C%20voice%20data%2C%20and%20texts%2C%20and%20is%20programmable%20by%20an%20encrypted%20app%20on%20a%20mobile%20or%20tablet%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20make%20a%20very%20scalable%20and%20affordable%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Rudominski%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20scalability%20is%20a%20big%20point%20because%20we%20only%20use%20commercial%20off-the-shelf%20components.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Himera%20told%20Ukrainian%20news%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilitarnyi.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fhimera-produces-up-to-1-000-radio-stations-per-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilitarnyi%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%20that%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bproducing%20up%20to%201%2C000%20radios%20per%20month%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20had%20the%20capacity%20to%20%26quot%3Bscale%20quickly%20to%202%2C500%20units.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20large-scale%20orders%2C%20we%20are%20prepared%20to%20supply%2010%2C000%20to%2015%2C000%20radios%20per%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223239%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Himera%20G1%20Pro%20is%20tailored%20to%20defense%20forces'%20needs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d4536069253ccddf994b3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Himera%20G1%20Pro.%3Cp%3EHIMERA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInnovation%20has%20been%20crucial%20to%20Kyiv's%20fight%20against%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20forces%2C%20and%20Ukrainian%20firms%20have%20continually%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20battlefield's%20ever-evolving%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERudominski%20told%20BI%20that%20this%20had%20also%20been%20key%20to%20Himera's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20we've%20done%20more%20than%2080%20versions%20of%20firmware%20updates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20more%20than%20probably%2020%20versions%20of%20separate%20kinds%20of%20hardware%20products.%20Most%20of%20them%20didn't%20go%20into%20production%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20have%20at%20some%20capacity%20been%20tested%20on%20the%20battlefield.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3