walking%20through%20the%20first%20and%20second%20floors%20of%20the%20museum%2C%20taking%20my%20time%20to%20study%20exhibits%20on%20the%20town's%20history%20of%20diamond%20mining%20and%20Chica%20da%20Silva's%20folkloric%20impact%20on%20Brazil%2C%20I%20walked%20outside%20to%20the%20back%20courtyard.%20I%20was%20overjoyed%20that%20I'd%20made%20it%20to%20my%20namesake's%20home.%20That's%20when%20I%20met%20a%20staff%20gardener%20who%20offered%20to%20show%20me%20something%20off%20the%20typical%20tour%3A%20Chica%20da%20Silva's%20garden.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20and%20I%20followed%20him%20along%20a%20stone%20path%2C%20stopping%20to%20try%20an%20orange%2C%20mint%20leaf%2C%20and%20sugar%20cane%20cut%20fresh%20from%20the%20stalk.%20As%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-home-garden-no-experience-save-money-on-groceries-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eavid%20plant%20lover%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20spontaneous%20garden%20tour%20felt%20like%20a%20dream%2C%20as%20though%20my%20namesake%20was%20personally%20rewarding%20me%20for%20making%20the%20journey%20in%20homage%20to%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gardener%20told%20me%20his%20name%20is%20John%20Lennon%20%E2%80%94%20his%20mom%20was%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20The%20Beatles.%20My%20jaw%20dropped%20in%20shock.%20Here%20I%20was%2C%20four%20thousand%20miles%20away%20from%20home%2C%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20Brazilian%20woman%20whom%20I'm%20named%20after%2C%20and%20the%20person%20showing%20me%20around%20is%20also%20named%20after%20an%20international%20luminary%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20British%20musicians%20in%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20stood%20in%20Chica's%20garden%2C%20in%20disbelief%20of%20my%20good%20fortune%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20wish%20the%20same%20fate%20for%20my%20new%20friend.%20Hopefully%2C%20one%20day%2C%20the%20Brazilian%20John%20Lennon%20will%20be%20able%20to%20visit%20Liverpool%20and%20walk%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20artist%20who%20inspired%20his%20name.%20I%20know%20from%20experience%20it'll%20be%20a%20life-changing%20journey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-gave-me-brazilian-name-with-americanized-spelling-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745067842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5763e3fe8d39283627abd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-gave-me-brazilian-name-with-americanized-spelling-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20watching%20%26quot%3BXica%20da%20Silva%26quot%3B%20my%20parents%20decided%20to%20name%20me%20Sheeka.%20No%20one%20can%20get%20the%20spelling%20right%20despite%20it%20being%20spelled%20phonetically.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sheeka%20Sanahori)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-gave-me-brazilian-name-with-americanized-spelling-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20have%20a%20supply%20of%20points%20for%20emergencies%20on%20my%20travel%20rewards%20credit%20card%20so%20I%20can%20go%20anywhere%20on%20a%20moment's%20notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-rewards-credit-card-makes-easy-plan-emergencies-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%2