sfully%20completed%20installations%20for%20various%20clients%2C%20from%20bungalows%20to%20schools.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20keen%20on%20exploring%20grid-free%20community%20solar%20setups%20for%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shilpa%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9%20much-needed%20reforms%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rooftop%20solar%20push%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20founders%20agree%20that%20while%20rooftop%20solar%20installations%20in%20India%20show%20promising%20growth%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20reforms.%20Based%20on%20their%20experience%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20they%20highlight%20key%20areas%20where%20reforms%20could%20significantly%20enhance%20the%20solar%20energy%20landscape%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Decentralised%20energy%20systems%20and%20local%20governance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanveer%20says%20solar%20projects%20work%20best%20when%20local%20communities%20are%20in%20charge.%20Giving%20people%20control%20makes%20the%20system%20more%20sustainable%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20He%20suggests%20that%20community%20ownership%20models%2C%20where%20villagers%20pay%20a%20nominal%20maintenance%20fee%2C%20can%20enhance%20responsibility%20and%20ensure%20the%20longevity%20of%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Ftanveer-solar-7-1744119917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanveer%20believes%20developing%20local%20technician-training%20initiatives%20can%20empower%20communities%20to%20maintain%20their%20own%20systems.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Ftanveer-solar-7-1744119917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Ftanveer-solar-7-1744119917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C