%20to%20come%20in%20here%2C%20how%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20into%20the%20forest%20in%20a%20way%20that%20disturbs%20it%3F%20Considering%20this%20is%20a%20hill%20slope%2C%20another%20concern%20was%20how%20not%20to%20disturb%20the%20flow%20of%20water.%20The%20third%20was%20the%20reptiles.%20Once%20people%20began%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20path%2C%20they%20would%20interact%20with%20the%20snakes%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20that.%20The%20best%20approach%20was%20to%20lift%20the%20path%20off%20the%20forest%20floor.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20and%20the%20team%20wanted%20to%20draw%20upon%20conventional%20wisdom%20and%20use%20sal%20wood%20that%20has%20been%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20for%20years%2C%20they%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386381%2Fpunjab-parminder-singh-turning-agri-waste-into-eco-friendly-tiles-prevent-stubble-burning-air-pollution-delhi-ncr-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20more%20sustainable%20bet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20zeroed%20in%20on%20teak%20grown%20in%20Kerala%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20durable%20and%20does%20not%20need%20polishing%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20support%20the%20walkway%20from%20below%20with%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20lightweight%2C%20sleeker%2C%20and%20easier%20to%20maintain%20over%20time.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20concrete%20because%20it%20would%20mess%20the%20forest%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20brainwave%2C%20every%20idea%2C%20and%20every%20decision%20has%20led%20to%20this%20beautiful%20composite%20that%20is%20the%20walkway.%20To%20say%20that%20Rahul%20has%20built%20Mumbai%20a%20walkway%20will%20be%20to%20trivialise%20what%20he%20has%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20I%20see%20it%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20given%20every%20person%20in%20this%20city%20a%20customised%20gift.%20To%20th